    dc:description "Figure 1. Light micrographs of the myxospore of Unicapsulocaudum mugilum sp. nov. (a) and (b) are developing stages (a is junior stage); (c–h) are mature spores of Unicapsulocaudum mugilum sp. nov. Scale bar = 10 μm." ;
